                    <span>He is a real Russian hero and ironically an American. Honest and fearless, he was doing it all for Russia which he truely loved. My condolences go to his family, people who knew and understood Paul....</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A good guy</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
